# GC Throwback Photo Contest

**Monday, January 8, 2024**

Event Name    : **GC Throwback Photo Contest: 25th Founding Anniversary of Gordon College**

Theme             :       **GC@25: Sustaining Inclusivity, Living with Values of Equity and Responsiveness**

**Mechanics**

1. This contest is open to all/ public;
2. Only **one (1) entry is allowed** per contestant;
3. Must be an **original photo** coming from the contestant;
4. **Acceptable** photos are:  
    • Photo captures using mobile phone;  
    • Photo captured by film camera and digicam;  
    • High Dynamic Range from several expos

