5. **Not acceptable** photos are:  
    • Photos which utilized photo tools and effects;  
    • Photo captured by fisheye lens;  
    • Stitched panoramas;  
    • Photo manipulation
6. **Allowable** photo post-processing:  
    • Cropping  
    • Color enhancements;  
    • Shadows and enhancements.
